{"data":[{"date":"15:01 23/07","title":"Bayern b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 mua Vidal cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/5/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Inter Milan \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mua Vidal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League sau v\u00e0i n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng, Inter Milan quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 Radja Nainggolan v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 38 tri\u1ec7u Euro bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 Davide Santon v\u00e0 Nicolo Zaniolo t\u1edbi AS Roma theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Nerazzurri \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Sime Vrsaljko c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/5/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bayern mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Vidal gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nInter t\u1eebng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Vidal song \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu th\u1ed1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. Nh\u1eefng Thiago Alcantara, Javi Martinez, Leon Goretzka, Sebastian Rudy, Corentin Tolisso v\u00e0 Renato Sanches \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Vidal ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y song kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e3i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria mu\u1ed1n 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Inter 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngo\u00e0i Inter, h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m AC Milan c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang kh\u00e1t ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Vidal. Cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Chile l\u00ean \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Uli Hoeness c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Serie A tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lazio-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-alex-iwobi-172-191833.html\">Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-nham-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-lich-su-mu-thay-pjanic-172-191831.html\">Juventus nh\u1eafm b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed MU thay Pjanic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-len-53-trieu-bang-172-191762.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jeremie-boga-roi-chelsea-toi-sassuolo-172-191736.html\">T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1546","checkdouble":"191832"},{"date":"14:52 23/07","title":"Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \"r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\" Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/lazio-bat-ngo-hoi-mua-alex-iwobi.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lazio mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Iwobi c\u1ee7a Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria.</h2><h2>Lazio chi 25 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Iwobi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Alex Iwobi ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 22 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn anh ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 39 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/1/Lazio-muon-mua-Alex-Iwobi-voi-gia-25-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"Lazio mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Iwobi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Lazio mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Iwobi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lazio mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Iwobi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Lazio mu\u1ed1n mua Alex Iwobi c\u1ee7a Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 25 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia v\u1eeba b\u00e1n Felipe Anderson cho West Ham v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42.5 tri\u1ec7u euro, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Lazio nh\u1eafm Iwobi c\u1ee7a Arsenal nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLazio tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Arsenal nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lazio c\u00f3 Iwobi l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Il Messaggero kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lazio chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alex Iwobi \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y Iwobi ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/11/Lazio-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" title=\"Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" alt=\"Lazio b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Lazio c\u00f3 Iwobi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Lazio \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlex Iwobi v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Arsenal, ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Singapore tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Iwobi ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao. HLV Emery \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Iwobi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nzonzi t\u1eeb Sevilla.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1545","checkdouble":"191833"},{"date":"15:32 23/07","title":"Sau Mahrez, Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 th\u00eam \"bom t\u1ea5n\" 100 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/24/sau-mahrez-man-city-sap-co-them-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp trung m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nV\u0103n To\u00e0n nhu\u1ed9m t\u00f3c th\u1eddi trang<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (22/7), c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf HAGL, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 12 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, bao g\u1ed3m 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u00e0 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n, V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, T\u1ea5n Sinh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 SLNA ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0o \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\" title=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/van-toan-xuat-hien-voi-kieu-dau-dam-chat-son-tung-mtp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n &ndash; ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf HAGL. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh \u0111\u00e3 nhu\u1ed9m m\u00e1i t\u00f3c \u0111en c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u00e0u kh\u00f3i x\u00e1m, v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i may m\u1eafn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 thua SLNA 1-3 t\u1ea1i V-League, v\u00e0 V\u0103n To\u00e0n mu\u1ed1n thay t\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0o cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u1ed1c H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng hay kh\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f3c&hellip; l\u00e0 x\u1ecbt, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba &ndash; m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng qu\u00e1 sa \u0111\u00e0 v\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Paulo Dybala c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda V\u0103n To\u00e0n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc theo &hellip; S\u01a1n T\u00f9ng M-TP, m\u1ed9t ca s\u0129 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn trung t\u00e2m PVF \u1edf H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\">Nh\u1eefng ai trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u00f9ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1544","checkdouble":"191834"},{"date":"16:04 23/07","title":"Chelsea c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/3/15/them-mot-ngoi-sao-dem-hung-tin-toi-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</h2><h2>Real quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/Khong-de-de-Real-Madrid-dua-Eden-Hazard-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mua Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Los Blancos c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2020, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n chia tay s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Hazard c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Hazard t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard.jpg\" title=\"Sarri mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea\" alt=\"Sarri muon bien Hazard thanh trung tam trong loi choi cua Chelsea\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Hazard b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mirror, Chelsea \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. HLV Sarri y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 The Blues gi\u1eef Hazard b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real Madrid, ngay c\u1ea3 khi Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard v\u1edbi Chelsea c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 2 n\u0103m, n\u1ebfu The Blues ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Real \u00e9p gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u00ednh to\u00e1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Mirror, gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Hazard \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 80 \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, b\u1edfi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 12 th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1543","checkdouble":"191840"},{"date":"16:27 23/07","title":"MU ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu...","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Manchester Evening News \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Martial</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-canh-bao-real-madrid-vu-eden-hazard-172-191840.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Bernabeu. D\u00f9 The Blues kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/mu-chi-ban-anthony-martial-neu.jpg\" title=\"MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Hazard k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a M.U l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues nh\u1eafm thay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Martial, \u00f4ng nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge. Chelsea tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Bayern Munich, Real Madrid v\u00e0 PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 r\u1eddi Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Anthony Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song M.U \u0111ang l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/martial-co-tiem-nang-tro-thanh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\" title=\"Martial chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft\" alt=\"Martial chiem tron mat bao trong lan dau ra mat\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, song M.U c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Manchester Evening News, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester mu\u1ed1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Martial \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Mourinho d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft ra \u0111i, MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Manchester Evening News kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 <br>\r\nti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Chelsea hay Bayern s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Martial hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1542","checkdouble":"191841"},{"date":"16:53 23/07","title":"V\u0103n To\u00e0n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ki\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t... S\u01a1n T\u00f9ng M-TP","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/van-toan-xuat-hien-voi-kieu-dau-dam-chat-son-tung-mtp.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp trung m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nV\u0103n To\u00e0n nhu\u1ed9m t\u00f3c th\u1eddi trang<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua (22/7), c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf HAGL, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n To\u00e0n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 12 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, bao g\u1ed3m 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL v\u00e0 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n, V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng, T\u1ea5n Sinh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 SLNA ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0o \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\" title=\"V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/van-toan-xuat-hien-voi-kieu-dau-dam-chat-son-tung-mtp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u0103n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n &ndash; ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf HAGL. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, anh \u0111\u00e3 nhu\u1ed9m m\u00e1i t\u00f3c \u0111en c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u00e0u kh\u00f3i x\u00e1m, v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i may m\u1eafn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 thua SLNA 1-3 t\u1ea1i V-League, v\u00e0 V\u0103n To\u00e0n mu\u1ed1n thay t\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0o cho ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u1ed1c H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng hay kh\u00f4ng, b\u1edfi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f3c&hellip; l\u00e0 x\u1ecbt, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba &ndash; m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0ng qu\u00e1 sa \u0111\u00e0 v\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Paulo Dybala c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0u t\u00f3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda V\u0103n To\u00e0n To\u00e0n thay \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc theo &hellip; S\u01a1n T\u00f9ng M-TP, m\u1ed9t ca s\u0129 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn trung t\u00e2m PVF \u1edf H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\">Nh\u1eefng ai trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tr\u00f9ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 13 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-so-bi-quay-lung-ngay-truoc-them-asiad-2018-292-191795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb quay l\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1541","checkdouble":"191843"},{"date":"17:14 23/07","title":"Ibra g\u1ea5y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m... T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/ibra-gay-soc-voi-tuyen-bo-muon-lam-tong-thong-my.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t y\u00eau th\u00edch. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00f2i l\u00e0m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9 trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIbra ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1981 \u0111ang h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp LA Galaxy h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ai nghi ng\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Zlatan Ibrahimovic, nh\u01b0ng anh lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111ang ti\u1ebfc r\u1ebb v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp MLS trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. B\u1edfi n\u1ebfu g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb l\u00e2u, anh t\u1ef1 tin m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m&hellip; T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9 nh\u01b0 Donald Trump l\u00fac n\u00e0y. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u01b0? T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang l\u00e0m c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i LA Galaxy m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eeb 10 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea3 qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00f2i l\u00e0m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9\" title=\"Ibrahimovic trong mau ao LA Galaxy\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/ibra-gay-soc-voi-tuyen-bo-muon-lam-tong-thong-my.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00f2i l\u00e0m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Donald Trump \u01b0? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m l\u1eafm. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 gia nh\u1eadp Nh\u00e0 tr\u1eafng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Hi\u1ebfn ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng. T\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u1edf qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 cha m\u1eb9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng sau 15 tr\u1eadn kho\u00e1c \u00e1o LA Galaxy, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 36 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n hu\u00eanh hoang v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u01a1 s\u1edf cho nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n ng\u00f4ng cu\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1eebng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00f2i l\u00e0m T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng M\u1ef9, anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i quay l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1i \u0111\u00e3. V\u1ee5 thua c\u01b0\u1ee3c David Beckham trong tr\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, khi Ibra ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn SV\u0110 Wembley \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu-172-191638.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ibra-tiet-lo-nguyen-nhan-buoc-phai-roi-mu-172-191638.html\">Ibra ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi M.U</span><br>\r\nSau khi y\u00ean \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i MLS, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Zlatan Ibrahimovic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-191326.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-khen-pogba-sau-danh-hieu-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-191326.html\">Ibrahimovic khen Pogba sau danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nZlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho Pogba sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00eam qua.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1540","checkdouble":"191844"},{"date":"16:52 23/07","title":"Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/12/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Roma mua Petr Cech thay Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Roma b\u00e1n Alisson cho Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 thu v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/12/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech.jpg\" title=\"Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay Alisson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Roma nh\u1eafm Petr Cech thay Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRoma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 36 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Olympico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Leno t\u1eeb Bundesliga, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Petr Cech b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda. Roma tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n sinh n\u0103m 1982 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Cech l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Arsenal b\u00e1n Cech, Roma ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 36 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Petr Cech</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Roma chi ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, song h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Chelsea trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech-172-191487.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech</span> trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/chelsea-muon-tai-ngo-petr-cech.jpg\" title=\"Cech\" alt=\"Cech\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cech c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Roma v\u00e0 Chelsea c\u00f9ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 36 tu\u1ed5i \u01b0u ti\u00ean tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Cech \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng \u1edf London, anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Petr Cech, Roma s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Mignolet c\u1ee7a Liverpool. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Anfield sau khi The Kop \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1539","checkdouble":"191845"},{"date":"17:16 23/07","title":"Leicester ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/5/leicester-phu-phang-voi-gary-cahill.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</h2><h2>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Gary Cahill</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Gary Cahill c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea t\u1eeb Bolton v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Blues. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/5/leicester-phu-phang-voi-gary-cahill.jpg\" title=\"Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Cahill</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-san-sang-chia-tay-cahill-172-191493.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Gary Cahill </span>\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 15 \u0111\u1ebfn 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Cahill, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Leicester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Jonny Evans t\u1eeb West Brom song Leicester v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Cahill trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hary Maguire c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m Gary Cahill</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/cahill.PNG\" title=\"cahill\" alt=\"cahill\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Leicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua Cahill</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m Cahill, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Leicester s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef Harry Maguire \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng M.U chi t\u1edbi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb Leicester kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb Gary Cahill s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi b\u1edfi HLV Sarri v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Rugani t\u1eeb Juventus. Hi\u1ec7n West Ham, Everton v\u00e0 Southampton l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Cahill.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1538","checkdouble":"191846"},{"date":"17:42 23/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 23/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/19/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-2307.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 23/07. </h2><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2307--hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2307  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2307  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>AC Mian c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGazzetta dello Sport tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 AC Milan c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri nh\u1eafm thay Morata.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Leicester ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gary Cahill r\u1eddi Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRoma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao 36 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm thay Courtois.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech-172-191845.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/12/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech-172-191845.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal</span><br>\r\n<span>Roma mu\u1ed1n mua Petr Cech thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Alisson \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea.jpg\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mundo Deportivo, Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 50, 53 v\u00e0 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Anthony Martial cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nExpress Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Anthony Martial cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0 Chelsea hay Tottenham, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe mu\u1ed1n PSG mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL'Equipe \u0111\u01b0a tin, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi PSG k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi N'Golo Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. <br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1ee5 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. The Blues s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ngay c\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-canh-bao-real-madrid-vu-eden-hazard-172-191840.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/3/15/them-mot-ngoi-sao-dem-hung-tin-toi-cho-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-canh-bao-real-madrid-vu-eden-hazard-172-191840.html\">Chelsea c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1ee5 Eden Hazard</span><br>\r\n<span>Real Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Eden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea, song The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh thay Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/David-Moyes-phat-bieu-ve-Jordan-Pickford-hinh-anh.jpg\" title=\"thu mon Pickford\" alt=\"thu mon Pickford\" style=\"border: none\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Pickford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm thay Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Jordan Pickford v\u00e0 Jack Butland trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois t\u1edbi Real. Trong s\u1ed1 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Blues c\u00f3 Butland cao h\u01a1n Pickford.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea v\u1ee5 Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus, song h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Mirror kh\u1eb3ngd \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1537","checkdouble":"191849"},{"date":"09:33 23/07","title":"Klopp khen ng\u1ee3i sao Dortmund sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/klopp-khen-ngoi-sao-dortmund-sau-tran-thua-cua-liverpool.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKarius gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 sai l\u1ea7m tai h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Karius tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u l\u00e0 \u201cLord\u201d, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1ed7i khi c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ecu m\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u201cKarius nh\u1eadp\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3. Sau tr\u1eadn, Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i post tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram nh\u01b0 sau.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m vui ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean n\u1ed7i \u0111au kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n cho h\u1ecd. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 th\u00f9 gh\u00e9t. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1eebng x\u1ea5u t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Thu-mon-Loris-Karius-dap-tra-chi-trich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Iker Casillas c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Loris Karius. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Porto chia s\u1ebb: \u201cNh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o Karius bao gi\u1edd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t? C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Karius?\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cH\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00ean! C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4i, nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta v\u1eady\u201d \u2013 c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, d\u00f9 Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u2013 khi \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a khi anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool-172-190518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool-172-190518.html\">Klopp: Karius b\u1ecb sang ch\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nKlopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua Real...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1536","checkdouble":"191819"},{"date":"10:45 23/07","title":"Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/mourinho-thua-nhan-mukhong-the-mua-them-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, HLV Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u00ean TTCN, v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 M.U kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, khi th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt. Ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngay t\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Mourinho cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i th\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn Los Angeles, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 5 tr\u1eadn, kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u00e0 quay l\u1ea1i Manchester. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf Los Angeles nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd \u0111ang \u1edf San Jose. Trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn MU kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn MU kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Kha-nang-lon-MU-khong-mua-them-tan-binh-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1edbn M.U kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa man trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, M.U c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o Alexis Sanchez h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, sau nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c xin visa. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ri\u00eang v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng theo quan s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Alexis ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat th\u1eddi gian.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh Fred, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Lee Grant. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 M.U kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial-172-191818.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial-172-191818.html\">MU l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c m\u00f9a h\u00e8...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my-172-191817.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/Kha-nang-lon-MU-khong-mua-them-tan-binh-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my-172-191817.html\">Mourinho b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9?</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a khi \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1535","checkdouble":"191821"},{"date":"11:30 23/07","title":"Karius: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea1i cho nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/karius-lan-dau-tien-phan-ung-ve-nhung-chi-trich.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKarius gay g\u1eaft v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">2 sai l\u1ea7m tai h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Karius tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 c\u01b0\u1eddi. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u l\u00e0 \u201cLord\u201d, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1ed7i khi c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ecu m\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 \u201cKarius nh\u1eadp\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3. Sau tr\u1eadn, Karius \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i post tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram nh\u01b0 sau.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m vui ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, c\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean n\u1ed7i \u0111au kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n cho h\u1ecd. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 th\u00f9 gh\u00e9t. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1eebng x\u1ea5u t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Thu-mon-Loris-Karius-dap-tra-chi-trich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Iker Casillas c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Loris Karius. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Porto chia s\u1ebb: \u201cNh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o Karius bao gi\u1edd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t? C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ee9 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Karius?\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cH\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00ean! C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4i, nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta v\u1eady\u201d \u2013 c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, d\u00f9 Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i \u2013 khi \u0111em v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 Karius \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a khi anh b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-nhung-con-so-cho-thay-su-ap-dao-cua-alisson-voi-karius-172-191639.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Alisson v\u1edbi Karius</span><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trang th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Opta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 so s\u00e1nh Alisson v\u1edbi Karius.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool-172-190518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool-172-190518.html\">Klopp: Karius b\u1ecb sang ch\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</span><br>\r\nKlopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua Real...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1534","checkdouble":"191822"},{"date":"09:22 23/07","title":"V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a \"l\u00ean m\u00e2y\" sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/37644906_1127134190773741_5719358041116114944_n.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn.</h2><h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khen ng\u1ee3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu mon Dang Van Lam\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/37644906_1127134190773741_5719358041116114944_n.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 20 V-League, CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0 song nh\u1edd tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00ean sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra v\u1ec1 an to\u00e0n sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n &lsquo;bay l\u01b0\u1ee3n&rsquo; c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Ho\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen d\u00e0nh cho anh sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: &ldquo;H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y L\u00e2m &quot;T\u00e2y&quot; \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 l\u1ea7n c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u Nga, \u00f4ng V\u00f5 \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00e2n, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League, c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c &lsquo;\u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh&rsquo; B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;&#10;color:#222222\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1533","checkdouble":"191823"},{"date":"11:34 23/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 23/7: M.U \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ngay-hom-nay-237.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (23/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2>M.U \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 237, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 237, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-167,-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alex Sandro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Duncan Castles ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, MU \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus, trong s\u1ef1 tranh \u0111ua quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a MU ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i PSG, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0u Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c, v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro h\u00f2ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \"l\u1eadt k\u00e8o\" c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Juventus kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch b\u00e1n Alex Sandro, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1 cao. MU \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Alex Sandro. V\u00ec anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf Juventus, n\u00ean MU d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng n\u00f3i: Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i cho b\u1ea1n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a MU, PSG c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alex Sandro khi \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 MU h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi Alex Sandro\".</div>\r\n<h2>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi HLV Julen Lopetegui r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cho Real 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ee5 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng Gia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh ch\u01a1i 36 tr\u1eadn cho Real nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn l\u00e0 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Real, gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00ed do t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mateo-kovacic-yeu-cau-duoc-roi-real-madrid-180-191805.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Maurizio Sarri c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua 3 ng\u00f4i sao Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Fali Ramadani sang Italy \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Juventus v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Gonzalo Higuain, Daniele Rugani \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Miralem Pjanic. Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Chelsea d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecfi mua Higuain v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u euro, Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi Miralem Pjanic c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi Higuain l\u00e0 Juve v\u00e0 Chelsea ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1. V\u1edbi Rugani, Juve c\u00f3 v\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n. V\u1edbi Pjanic, Juve \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 237 MU \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 237 MU \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Alex Sandro  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-237-MU-da-nhan-duoc-cai-gat-dau-cua-Alex-Sandro--hinh-anh-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Milan nh\u1eafm mua 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1n quy\u1ebft cho ph\u00e9p d\u1ef1 Europa League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00f2a \u00e1n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ec3 thao (TAS), Milan l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u00f3 tin n\u00f3i Milan \u0111ang nh\u1eafm mua \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 trong 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00e0 Morata (Chelsea), Benzema (Real) v\u00e0 Higuain (Juventus). Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Benzema, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin anh mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Milan. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Higuain, Juve \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i 60 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t l\u00e0 30/7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Argentina. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Morata, anh mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Juve thay v\u00ec Milan.</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal mua l\u1ea1i Giroud sau n\u1eeda n\u0103m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sky Sports b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay ch\u00ednh Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Giroud sang Chelsea, n\u01a1i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea s\u1eafp mua trung phong Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus, Giroud c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ph\u00e9p tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal n\u1ebfu \u201cPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7\u201d mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h2>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca, v\u1ec1 Everton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trang web Goal.com cho bi\u1ebft trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t xong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Everton v\u00e0 gi\u1edd hai b\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd Barcelona \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. Mina kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i Barca m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng sau th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup cho \u0110T Colombia v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Everton Marco Silva.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca-180-191808.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/12/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca-180-191808.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca</span><br>\r\n<span>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca. Everton \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng anh gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona cho h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Karius s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean, Loris Karius v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u201cThe Kop\u201d v\u1eeba mua v\u1ec1 Alisson t\u1eeb AS Roma. \u201cLoris l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1532","checkdouble":"191825"}]}